Package: com.sinfool.incognitovideomode
Name: Incognito Video Mode
Author: Sinfool
Description: Makes the camera appear as if it's always in "Photo" mode by changing the shutter button & dial selected indicator to "Photo" mode style.  Also changes Video mode's top/bottom bar rotation/BG style to Photo mode style, hides the elapsed time, still photo & framerate buttons and adds top/bottom bar photo buttons when recording. Makes the camera appear as if it's always in "Photo" mode by changing the shutter button & dial selected indicator to "Photo" mode style.  Also changes Video mode's top/bottom bar rotation/BG style to Photo mode style, hides the elapsed time, still photo & framerate buttons and adds top/bottom bar photo buttons when recording.
 .
 IMPORTANT NOTE:  By default, the camera always opens in "Photo" mode so a single swipe over to "Video" mode is always necessary when opening the camera.
 .
 [v.1] Tested with an iPad mini 4 on 10.2.  Made as a request via r/jailbreak.  (4-11-17)
